metadata.title: VitaGravy Skin and Coat Supplement, Delicious Braised Salmon Flavor – For Cats of All Ages and Sizes – 11 Ounce, up to 44 Servings
features: VITAGRAVY SUPPLEMENT: Mix Vitagravy supplement into your cat’s favorite food to add nutrition to mealtime. Delicious Braised Salmon Flavor is a great, healthy treat for cats of all ages and sizes!
SKIN & COAT: Vitamin supplement in a tasty gravy nourishes dry, itchy skin and helps keep coats shiny. Can help reduce non-seasonal shedding
NUTRIENT-PACKED: Enriches mealtimes with healthy vitamins, minerals, and omega 3 & 6 fatty acids. Tasty flavor makes food more appetizing for picky eaters, elderly, and sick cats
RECOMMEDED USE: For cats of all ages and sizes. 11-ounce pouch contains about 44 servings for a 15-pound cat. Shake well before use, mix well with food, and refrigerate after opening
PRODUCT DETAILS: 11-ounce pouch Vitagravy supplement for Skin & Coat
description: VitaGravy Skin & Coat provides supplemental vitamins, minerals, and omega fatty acids. Delicious and hearty! A nutrient-rich boost concealed within a delicious gravy. Provides exciting variety at mealtime and is sure to have your cat begging for more! Low-fat and low-sodium. All-natural and human-grade with 100% vegetarian flavors. Each pouch is 325ml, (11 oz.). About 44 servings for a 15 lb. cat!
